{"tid":666713,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老真係隨時會害死人","createTime":"2018-05-16T06:17:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T06:26:27.000Z","uid":150100,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5a7c1bfbee6fa4f2e015f354e20b09cf6e719836","tid":666713,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:17:08.000Z","msg":"話說求先撘巴士，一上車已經好大陣油味，咁我開頭以為係有油漆工人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知坐坐下個司機叫啲人落車等其他車啦，因為架車有問題(我開頭都唔知做乜，聽緊歌)<br />\n屌，然後班廢老就屌個司機話咩架車仲行得㗎嘛de ne lu mei<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  叫佢繼續揸<br />\n然後我等車嗰陣見㗎巴士係咁漏啲油出嚟同噴煙<br />\n如果個司機真係繼續揸真係唔知會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw, 索油味索到胸口有啲郁悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c4645aadb5006c88df496411ff2bbaecada68be","tid":666713,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:18:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"151e814f00279111379b309ebce87320e1f0e75c","tid":666713,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:18:50.000Z","msg":"屌，胸口有啲痛，如果我不幸辭世，依篇就係我嘅遺言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12fdcdb86ee7713e9ec9cd9ad3c1daa6e357f841","tid":666713,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c4645aadb5006c88df496411ff2bbaecada68be","tid":666713,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:18:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3164544c5b90dc15989dbe02b151bb399f556b01","tid":666713,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wan